name: TableSelectionChangedEventArgs
description: Provides information about the table that raised the SelectionChanged event.

properties.name: type
properties.description: Gets the type of the event.

properties.name: isInsideTable
properties.description: Indicates if the selection is inside a table, address will be useless if IsInsideTable is false.

properties.name: worksheetId
properties.description: Gets the id of the worksheet in which the selection changed.

properties.name: tableId
properties.description: Gets the id of the table in which the selection changed.

properties.name: address
properties.description: Gets the range address that represents the selected area of the table on a specific worksheet.
